Package careerhub.models

Class CompanyRep

java.lang.Object
careerhub.models.User
careerhub.models.CompanyRep
public class CompanyRep extends User
Represents a Company Representative user in the Internship Management System. A Company Representative can create internship opportunities (up to a maximum of five), review student applications, approve or reject them, and toggle the visibility of their opportunities.

This class stores profile information (company name, department, position), approval status from Career Center Staff, and a list of internship IDs created by this representative. It also tracks the representativeâ€™s last-used filter settings for convenience when navigating menus.
